title: I Found a Hole in my Yard. It Might Be a Dungeon, but That’s Now my Garbage Dump - Novel Updates
tags: Business Management   Dungeons   Hard-Working Protagonist   Industrialization   Male Protagonist   Modern Day   Monsters   Organized Crime   Poor to Rich   Shameless Protagonist   Weak to Strong
author: Daisuke   ダイスケ
description:
One day, I found a hole in the yard of my house.
It was just the right for a garbage hole, so I threw my garbage in it.
I threw household waste in it.
I threw business waste in it.
I threw construction waste in it.
However, the hole is still not filled……>
